'''Michael Joe Jackson''' ({{bd|1958-ngièn|8-ngie̍t 29-ngit|2009-ngièn|6-ngie̍t 25-ngit}}), he [[Mî-koet]] yit-chak [[Fî-yí Mî-koet Het-ngìn|Het-ngìn]] [[kô-sú]], pûn ngìn ham-cho "liù-hàng yîm-ngo̍k chṳ̂ vòng" (King of Pop). Kì tui sṳ-kie [[yîm-ngo̍k]], [[vú-tho]] lâu [[sṳ̀-song]] tû yù tông thai kung-hien. Kì chhai 1982-ngièn fat-hàng ke yîm-ngo̍k liu̍k-yáng-tai ''Thriller'' mai-chhut 1.9 yi phién, chṳ kîm-ha hàn-he sṳ-kie mai-chhut chui tô ke [[yîm-ngo̍k chôn-si̍p]].

Kì chhai [[2009-ngièn]] [[6-ngie̍t 25-ngit]] chhai Mî-koet [[California]] ke [[Los Angeles]] ko-sṳ̂n.

